{"title":"ENVE Loam & Range Collection ‘Must Be Magic,’ Brand Says","link":"https://bikerumor.com/enve-loam-range-collection/","date":1681732825000,"content":"<p>Check out the ENVE Loam &amp; Range Collection, new this month for mountain bikers and gravel riders.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll find wind jackets, lightweight hoodies and midlayers, t-shirts, shorts, and pants for men and women in the lineup.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Standouts include the Last Resort Wind Jacket, which weighs in at a feathery 110 grams. Tear-resistant fabric and taped seams help it “fend off the heaviest of gales,” ENVE says. “It must be magic.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"cyclists on a hillside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ENVE_Windbreaker_Women-8806-copy-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For fairer weather, there’s the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/chicken-line-gives-women-the-easy-route-to-killer-mountain-bike-clothes/\" target=\"_blank\">Women’s</a> Composite Tank. Antibacterial fibers fight the funk, and a drop tail helps keep your lower back burn-free on long rides. The “Sage Lemonade” color pattern is, to some degree, a head-turner.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM.png\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-800x485.png\" alt=\"enve women's tank top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-800x485.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-297x180.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-120x73.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-768x466.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-1536x932.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screen-Shot-2023-03-30-at-2.58.43-PM-2048x1243.png 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And for bottoms, there’s the Women’s Trail Pant, with pleated knee pockets that accept pads, plus a tapered shape. Laser-cut vents “work in unison” on the fabric to cut the stagnation on hot slogs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the whole lineup on ENVE now.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.enve.com/product-category/loam-range-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">enve.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/enve-loam-range-collection/\">ENVE Loam &amp; Range Collection ‘Must Be Magic,’ Brand Says</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Sam Anderson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b537bebb5d80a76b3ee5fa3da45a2322e4141ecac2c1d760d0638a1ae16060b0","category":"Cycling"}